</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="75" pageNumber="470" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="75.[167,1374,292,1035]" pageId="75" pageNumber="470">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[167,402,607,640]" pageId="75" pageNumber="470">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Relatively long tail of the Volcano Forest Shrew suggests that it might be partly scansorial.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
